    "en": {
      "title": "Bus services back to normal in Yali",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jaffna of Sri Lanka Transport Board in Jaffna. The strike by the road workers has been abandoned.",
        "Meanwhile, Jaffna. Jaffna said that private buses will run at 50% from today in the district. P. Kengadaran, the head of the network of district and regional integrated bus companies, said.",
        "Jaffna. It is noteworthy that Sri Lankan Transport Board and private bus employees have been on strike for the past two days in the district. (a)"
      ],
